  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/b01f003021d851c332c23bb86dfaedf8.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Zeul”, an Internet installation technician</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >His company received an application for internet installation in the mail from a unique place called “Ruined Hospital”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zeul came to the hospital to install the internet with the question, \"Is there really such a place?\",</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But there were things waiting there that were as unbelievable as the hospital's name...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to play</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Explore the hospital by Thwarting the creatures that are trying to stop you and solving puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Successfully install the internet and surprise customer...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/3b9d0b6e487790a4c4a51f89485dd8e8.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=340 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various Nurse Creatures</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Various types of nurse creatures will try to stop you.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Thwart them and advance the story.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/b799e53ad133edb0bf6afc7bf5f0b350.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=340 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compelling Characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You can progress through the story with the compelling characters that exist here.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/ba627c89517c145fc7742e74680044ef.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=340 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FPS combat System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Defend yourself in a dark and dangerous hospital.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Collect bullets and various items to turn the battle in your favor.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/c64029da0b9db6e9ad406c4db4fae144.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=340 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Companion System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>As you progress through the story with Nell, you can battle together</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>and collect items by unlocking additional locations and puzzles.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/a389273de86de853c676b7e483117f8c.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interesting Story & Cutscenes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Join internet installer Zeul as he works to surprise his customers.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785280/extras/93dcc8494cc47197eaf7145071a0db76.avif?t=1734834299\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls & Various Puzzles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Solve puzzles throughout the hospital to complete your mission safely.</i></p></li></ul>",
